@Pencil 
For the last one, you can head on to hentainexus "Aspirations Against a Blue Sky" for the translated version. Was a pretty good read, not very fappable though.
Probably, the main reason they changed the magazine name is the change of publication schedule.
Read this months ago so I don't remember everything but the TL;DR Comic KOH rebooted into COMIC AOHA for those don't know. (Why? Like I told you, I don't remember shit hehe).
What the fuck happened in that last one?
